body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        To apply your projects ideas for the OSL Internship 2024 (1st Cycle),
        please fill this current form.

        You should be a core maintainer of the projects you list here, in order to apply them for the internship program.
        First, please read the the Internship Program documentation:
          https://opensciencelabs.org/programs/internship/

        All projects should have a Code of Conduct, and should be under any of the OSI Open Source Approved Licenses (https://opensource.org/licenses/).

        You can use this document as a reference for filling this form:
        https://github.com/OpenScienceLabs/grant-proposals/blob/main/gsoc/2023/osl-projects-ideas.md.
        This was the Projects Ideas we wrote for GSoC, and we are using the same format for
        OSL Internship Program.

        Links of Interesting:
        - Join our discord server: https://opensciencelabs.org/discord
        - Follow-us in our social media:
          - https://twitter.com/opensciencelabs
          - https://www.youtube.com/@opensciencelabs
          - https://www.linkedin.com/company/open-science-labs

  - type: input
    id: organization_name
    attributes:
      label: Organization/Project name
      description: The Organization/Project Name
      placeholder: ex: My Organization Name
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: organization_url
